 42266900 VULKAN : EGLSurfacelessContextTest.*/*ForceDelayedDeviceCreationForTesting* = SKIP
 
+500721361 VULKAN SWIFTSHADER : VertexAttributeTestES3.storeStaticAttribWithLargeOffset/* = SKIP
